No street signs are visible from here.	從這裡看不到任何街道標誌。
%s: dir %c loc %d,%d	%s: dir %c loc %d,%d
Error:  sideAlley at %d,%d not an object	Error:  sideAlley 在 %d,%d 不是物件
%s sign%sto the %s%sreads:  '%s'.  	%s 號誌%s，朝向%s%s，上面寫著：「%s」。
There is an unmarked alley%sto the %s.  	這裡有一條沒有標示的巷弄%s通往%s。
The sign on your street reads '%s'.	你這條街上的標誌寫著：「%s」。
You got some useful lockpicking practice, but the door has been bolted from the inside.  No amount of skill will allow you to open it.	你藉此練習了開鎖技巧，頗有收穫，但這扇門從裡面被閂死了。再高的技巧也無法把它打開。
Error: no alley index entry for room %d, heading %d	Error: 房間 %d、方向 %d 沒有巷弄索引項目
You hear the sounds of people standing in fear of their drab and wretched lives.	你聽見人們的聲音，充滿了對自己單調悲慘生活的恐懼。
These guards appear to be the strong, silent type.	這些衛兵看起來是那種沉默寡言的硬漢。
These guards could whip you like cream.	這些衛兵三兩下就能把你打得落花流水。
This street is closed by order of Khaveen.   No one is permitted to pass.	這條街已奉哈維因之命封閉。任何人不得通行。
Halt.  You are under arrest for speaking with a known subversive.  You will come with us.	站住。你因與已知的叛亂分子交談而被捕，跟我們走一趟。
Two more guards walk up behind you and "escort" you to the dungeon.  After some brutal questioning, you are just locked away for a long time.	又有兩名衛兵從你身後走來，「護送」你前往地牢。經過一番殘酷的審問後，你就這樣被關了很長一段時間。
You hear the sounds of people coming and going and living their lives.	你聽見人們來來往往、過著日常生活的聲音。
The mass of rock radiates strong magic.	這塊巨大的岩石散發著強烈的魔力。
Your attack has no effect on the stone of the Earth Elemental.	你的攻擊對土元素的岩石軀體毫無效果。
You have enough elemental dirt.	你已經有足夠的元素泥土了。
You can't be serious.  It is too big and dangerous right now.	你該不是認真的吧。牠現在太巨大也太危險了。
You carefully put the elemental away in the cloth bag.	你小心翼翼地把元素收進布袋裡。
The elemental earth keeps slipping through your hands, and you have nothing suitable to put it in.	這捧元素泥土不斷從你手中滑落，而你手邊沒有合適的容器可以裝它。
You hear a rumbling at the end of the alley...	你聽見巷弄盡頭傳來一陣轟隆聲……
That wouldn't help you now.	那現在幫不了你。
You quickly move into position in preparation for combat.	你迅速就定位，準備戰鬥。
The strange noise seems to be coming closer...	那陣怪聲似乎越來越近……
The software you are now using was produced through the efforts of many people: designers, artists, programmers, musicians, and lots of other hard-working professionals.  If you make copies of this software for any reason other than to make a personal backup, you are not only breaking the law, but raising the cost of software for all legitimate users.  PLEASE DO NOT MAKE ILLEGAL COPIES OF THIS GAME !	你現在使用的軟體，是由許多人共同努力完成的：設計師、美術人員、程式設計師、音樂家，以及許多辛勤工作的專業人士。如果你複製這套軟體，且目的並非僅供個人備份，你不僅觸犯法律，也會提高所有合法使用者的軟體成本。請勿非法複製本遊戲！
The city of Shapeir shines in the moonlight.	夏皮爾城在月光下閃耀著光芒。
